<HEADLINE> Cavaliers 82, Grizzlies 80  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    VANCOUVER, British Columbia (AP) -- Shawn Kemp scored five of his 24 points
in the final three minutes to lead the Cleveland Cavaliers to an 82-80 win over
the Vancouver Grizzlies on Friday night.
</P>
<P>
	   Brevin Knight added 16 points while Lamond Murray scored 13 as the Cavaliers
improved to 7-0 all-time against the Grizzlies.
</P>
