<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-15 01:35 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Details of GOP Presidential Debate  </HEADLINE>
   By The Associated Press
<TEXT>
<P>
	   Details of today's debate among Republican presidential candidates:
</P>
<P>
	   WHO: Gary Bauer, Texas Gov. George W. Bush, Steve Forbes, Sen. Orrin Hatch
of Utah, Alan Keyes and Sen. John McCain of Arizona.
</P>
<P>
	   WHEN: 2 p.m.-3:30 p.m. EST.
</P>
<P>
	   WHERE: Iowa Public Television, Johnston, Iowa.
</P>
<P>
	   SPONSOR: Des Moines Register.
</P>
<P>
	   MODERATOR: Des Moines Register's Dennis Ryerson.
</P>
<P>
	   COVERAGE: Live on CNN, FOX News Channel, C-SPAN.
