<HEADLINE> Gore's Daughter Hurt in Accident  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- The daughter of Vice President Gore was slightly injured
when another vehicle ran a red light and smashed into her car, police said
Saturday.
</P>
<P>
